## ðŸ“± What Is DanKPay?

DanKPay is a full-service blockchain payment system using a utility token ($DKBUD) on the Solana blockchain.  
It enables legal cannabis dispensaries to accept payments via QR code, Phantom wallet, and instant settlement â€” without needing cash or traditional banks.

